# Root safety net — never track secrets or personal data anywhere in this repo.
# (KloSportsBot/.gitignore has the project-specific list; this is belt-and-suspenders.)
**/auth.json
!**/auth.json.example
**/.env
**/bridge.config.sh
**/*.ndjson
**/*.log
**/state_*.txt
**/node_modules/
**/USER.md
**/MEMORY.md
**/*.png
.DS_Store
